les, mathematical posers and many more.\nSet on a relaxing tropical beach to keep you calm as you concentrate on solving the puzzles.", "short_description": "Puzzle Tropicana is a uniquely chilled-out collection of mental and physical puzzles.\nFeaturing a wide variety of challenges to tax the brain of all ages and abilities.\nNot just one type of puzzle...test yourself with a crazy collection of brain teasers.\nIncludes physics puzzles, jigsaws, musical challenges, picture puzzles, mathematical posers and many more.\nSet on a relaxing tropical beach to keep you calm as you concentrate on solving the puzzles."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://hypeknotgames.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://hypeknotgames.com/terms-of-use", "publisher_name": "Hypeknot", "support_website_url": "https://hypeknotgames.com/contact", "website_url": "https://hypeknotgames.com/puzzle-tropicana", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["PUZZLE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "759813868705976"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 0, "nodes": []}, "baseline_offer": null, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": []}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "5378998592121275", "version": "1.4"}, "id": "533510121597857", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "_